These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, november, january
3 different games are played: scrabble, poker, canasta
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, helicopter, ship
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris, poppy
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, bolivar, ritmeester
House: tower, gothic-revival, victorian
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, grey, azure
 1. the person who growspoppy is the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the victorian house##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the helicopter##1
 4. the tower house is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who growsiris##1
 6. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 8. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the person playing poker is the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | august  | november   | january      |
| Game          | canasta      | scrabble     | poker     |
| Transport           | helicopter | ship  | train   |
| Flower   | iris   | poppy     | zinnia  |
| Cigar   | bongani      | bolivar      | ritmeester      |
| House   | victorian      | gothic-revival    | tower   |
| Color         | fuchsia    | grey | azure |

