.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, whist, domino
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, old-henry, bolivar
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, tea, lemonade
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, mauve, blue
City: edinburgh, san-francisco, boston
House: townhouse, ranch-style, gothic-revival
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, pumpkin, cherry
 1. the person who likes mauve is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing domino is the townhouse house##1
 3. the person eating pumpkin is in the middle##1
 4. the person playing whist is the person traveling to boston##1
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the person who likes blue is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
 8. the person playing whist is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the far left##1
10. the bolivar-smoker is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
11. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Game         | whist | domino  | backgammon     |
| Cigar           | ritmeester        | old-henry | bolivar    |
| Beverage   | tea  | lemonade    | mirinda    |
| Color   | blue    | mauve    | red   |
| City           | boston        | san-francisco    | edinburgh        |
| House         | ranch-style     | townhouse  | gothic-revival     |
| Food     | cherry         | pumpkin       | cranberry |

