The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, r&b, funk
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, aquamarine, mauve
House: palace, art-deco, modern
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daisy, sunflower
3 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, scrabble
 1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 2. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the palace house##1
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
 6. the person who likes mauve is the ritmeester-smoker##1
 7. the fan of r&b is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
10. the fan of funk is the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Cigar      | ritmeester   | cain         | prince |
| City          | paris  | new-york        | san-francisco    |
| Music-Genre           | house | r&b  | funk  |
| Color   | mauve | lilac | aquamarine         |
| House   | art-deco | palace       | modern        |
| Flower           | bellflower       | daisy        | sunflower       |
| Game     | scrabble       | backgammon  | canasta       |

