The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, superhero, romance
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, ebony, aquamarine
There are 3 different nationalities: british, spanish, colombian
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia, balloon-flower
 1. the person who likes ebony is on the far right##1
 2. the colombian is the person who growsbegonia##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 5. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 6. the person who growsorchid is the person playing whist##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 8. the person playing domino is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 9. the person playing domino is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the british##1
11. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |        3        |
| City      | nizza | marseilles    | berlin           |
| Hobby          | rock-climbing  | hiking | filmmaking      |
| Game           | domino  | whist       | canasta |
