4. the person who growsballoon-flower is the fan of blues##1
5. the modern house is on the left of the tower house##1
6. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
7. the person who growsrose is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
8. the owner of the rat is the tower house##1
9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |
