.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-17::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, bellflower, zinnia
City: colone, rome, miami
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, chess
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, ritmeester, davidoff
There 3 different types of food: plum, kiwi, apricot
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, grey, red
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, turtle, horse
 1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is the person traveling to colone##1
