 5. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 6. the person playing scrabble is the person eating apricot##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 8. the person who likes red is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
10. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
11. the cain-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1

