3 different games are played: bridge, chess, poker
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, train, quad-bike
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, parkour, soccer
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the tower house##1
 2. the townhouse house is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the townhousecher is the person driving the roller##1
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the roller##1
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 9. the person playing poker is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is soccer is in the middle##1
11. the writer is on the far left##1

